            <h4 class="step-title">Step 1</h4>
            <h4>Install the rest2mobile plug-in</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Open Android Studio or IntelliJ IDEA, go to Preferences, Plugins, and choose <b>Install plugin from disk</b>. In
                the dialog that opens, select the Android plug-in you downloaded earlier. </li>
                <li>Click OK. Your IDE will restart.</li>
            </ul>
