            <h4 class="step-title">Step 2</h4>
            <h4>Generate Java code for your REST service</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>To generate Java code for your REST/JSON service, open the Magnet menu, and choose <b>Add REST API</b>.</li>
                <li>Enter the REST request, parameters, headers, and response if you have one, otherwise click <b>Test API</b> to generate one from the API.</li>
                <li>Click <b>Generate Service</b>.</li>
